Keep taking PNV - pt agrees with plan. ·Instructions: We will call you with your lab tests when we received them. Please call with any vaginal bleeding or pelvic pain., extended (4 or more elements), AS is a 20 yo who presents for missed cycle. She has not been seen since 2011. She reports normal menstrual cycles Q 30 days, no spotting between until LMP 2/23/20. She had 4 pregnancy tests at home they were all positive. She was also seen at a clinic in south chicago and had a positive pregnancy test there but no lab work or US. Today her urine pregnancy was negative in our clinic - she denies any bleedinf or carmping, no abnl vaginal discharge/odor/pruritis. No vaginal lesions. No fevers. CP, SOB, cough, wheezing.
